These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different games are played: chess, poker, domino, monopoly
4 different pets are kept: frog, rabbit, rat, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, skiing, volleyball
 1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
 2. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not the person playing monopoly##6
 5. the person playing domino is somewhere to the right of the person playing chess##5
 6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person playing poker##8
 8. the person playing poker is not the person who's sport is volleyball##6
 9. the person playing chess is not the owner of the snake##6
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the owner of the snake##1
11. the person playing poker is not to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##8
12. the person playing poker is in an even position##4
13. the person playing monopoly is not to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
14. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Game    | chess         | monopoly     | domino     | poker         |
| Pet   | rabbit | snake    | rat     | frog |
| Sport   | cycling       | ice-hockey | volleyball | skiing       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, zombie, superhero, family
There are 4 different nationalities: german, spanish, canadian, thai
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, ice-hockey, weightlifting
 1. the canadian is not to the right of the thai##8
 2. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 4. the person watching family movies is the spanish##1
 5. the german is not the person watching superhero movies##6
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 7. the person watching family movies is on the right of the german##1
 8. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 9. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
10. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero          | satire      | family      | zombie   |
| Nationality        | canadian     | german | spanish | thai      |
| Sport      | weightlifting | baseball    | badminton  | ice-hockey |

