.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, february, january, june
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, country, d&b, techno
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, chinese, pakistani, mexican
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the mexican##1
 2. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the pakistani##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 4. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5
 5. the dutch is not the fan of blues##6
 6. the fan of blues is on the left of the mexican##1
 7. the fan of blues is not to the right of the fan of techno##8
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4
10. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Birthday         | january  | february | june | november |
| Music-Genre   | country  | blues      | techno | d&b        |
| Nationality     | dutch | pakistani       | mexican    | chinese     |

