.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, horror, mystery, thriller
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, puzzles, cooking, gardening
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, emerald, yellow, red
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 2. the person who likes emerald is not to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##8
 3. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the person watching crime movies##5
 4. the person watching crime movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching horror movies is not to the right of the person who likes emerald##8
 6. the person who likes yellow is not to the right of the person watching thriller movies##8
 7. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
 8. the person who likes red is somewhere to the right of the person who likes emerald##5
 9. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is the person who likes yellow##1
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | thriller | horror    | mystery |
| Hobby   | cooking    | puzzles     | card-games   | gardening     |
| Color   | ebony | yellow   | emerald | red    |

