.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, hiking, reading
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, july, february, march
City: new-york, venice, colone, paris
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to venice##5
 2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is not the person who's hobby is hiking##6
 7. the person who's hobby is card-games is not the person traveling to colone##6
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is the person traveling to colone##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
10. the person traveling to paris is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
11. the person traveling to paris is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | hiking       | card-games | gardening  | reading    |
| Birthday   | february       | march    | july | october    |
| City         | paris | new-york   | colone   | venice |

