.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, sailing, biathlon, skiing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, documentary, horror
4 different games are played: backgammon, whist, go, mah-jongg
 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the left of the person watching action movies##8
 2. the person watching horror movies is not the person playing whist##6
 3. the person playing go is somewhere between the person who's sport is sailing and the person watching horror movies##7
 4. the person playing whist is not to the left of the person watching crime movies##8
 5. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
 6. the person playing go is the person watching action movies##1
 7. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person watching documentary movies##5
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person playing go##2
 9. the person watching horror movies is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##8
11. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Sport          | sailing      | biathlon      | skiing | cycling |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action    | horror | crime     |
| Game   | backgammon    | go | mah-jongg  | whist |

