 4. the pilot is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 5. the project-manager is on the left or right of the person who likes ebony##3
 6. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the person driving the train is not the person who likes yellow##6
 8. the social-worker is not to the right of the person who likes yellow##8
 9. the person who likes yellow is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
10. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
11. the social-worker is not to the left of the person who likes yellow##8
12. the pilot is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
13. the pilot is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4      |
