There are 4 different nationalities: german, indonesian, malaysian, pakistani
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, crime, fantasy, family
 1. the designer is not to the right of the person watching superhero movies##8
 2. the pakistani is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the malaysian##7
 3. the police-officer is not to the left of the person watching crime movies##8
 4. the person watching crime movies is on the far left##1
 5. the dancer is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the german is not to the left of the designer##8
 7. the pakistani is on the left or right of the german##3
 8. the german is somewhere to the right of the dancer##5
 9. the police-officer is not to the left of the person watching superhero movies##8
10. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the left of the police-officer##8
11. the german is not to the left of the dressmaker##8
12. the police-officer is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
13. the german is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5
14. the dressmaker is on the left of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
| Job         | dancer    | designer | dressmaker | police-officer    |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | pakistani    | german      | indonesian |
| Movie-Genre     | crime | superhero          | family      | fantasy       |

