 4. the coach is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
 5. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the architect##3
 6. the owner of the bird is the coach##1
 7. the bartender is not to the right of the coach##8
 8. the coach is not to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##8
 9. the coach is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
10. the coach is somewhere to the right of the bartender##5
