 5. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the right of the person who likes yellow##5
 6. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the right of the person who likes purple##5
 7. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 8. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
 9. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
10. the person eating cranberry is not to the right of the person who likes ivory##8
