The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, filmmaking, traveling, card-games
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, subway, taxi, tram
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
 4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person driving the boat is not the person drinking fanta##6
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
10. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the right of the person drinking fanta##8
11. the person drinking water is somewhere between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person driving the boat##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage           | mirinda  | water | fanta | hot-chocolate |
| Hobby   | traveling | card-games           | drawing  | filmmaking |
| Transport     | boat      | taxi           | tram     | subway  |

